title: Lg One Bdrm w/  Hrdwd Fls, Fiber Optic, Skylite in Hist. Row Hs
posting_body: ['Immaculate, Large Top Floor - Third Floor One Bedroom Apartment with Skylite, Hard Wood Floors, Original Wood Work and Private Entrance for $995/mo located in the Historic Clinton Row gas stove and refrigerator.', 'There is coin operated laundry on site.', 'All Utilities are paid in the rent except electric and cooking gas.', 'Heat is paid!.', 'Cable, High Speed Internet and Fiber Optic ready.', '***We offer in-person apartment tours and virtual apartment tours!', '***', 'We offer in-person apartment tours by meeting scheduled potential clients at the front door of the rental
